dct_title_s: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of Japan [copy 2]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Shows prefectures, cities, mountains, and roads of Japan. Insets: Outline map of Japan -- Ezo and Chisima -- Ryukyu Islands -- South extension of Osumi Province -- Island of Formosa. In upper margin: Library atlas of the world. [Japan.]. 85-86. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912.
